r 1600m at Eagle Farm as the favourite last start when trying to lead all of the way. Winner of a recent six-runner trial which should see him jump as the favourite and prove hard to beat. 4. VALENCIA ROC resumes from a spell of eight months. Having her first start from a new stable after having placed in all five runs last prep, including last start over 1400m at Eagle Farm after racing on the speed to the turn. Placed second here fresh-up last prep over today's distance and rates well as a main danger. 5. YOWERI resumes from a spell following a last start fourth of eight over 1200m at Gosford. Having his first start from the Tony Gollan stable and having placed second of eight in a recent 1000m trial at this track is well worth a second look. 8. ARISTOCRATIC GIRL drifted well back in the running last start before coming home strongly to finish third of six over 1000m at Eagle Farm. Solid each-way prospect.\",\"runners\":[1,4,5,8],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,9,4,1]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,7,9]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,8,5]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,5,8]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,8,6]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,3,5,11]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,5,8]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":5,"venueMnemonic":"DBN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Fi